    "es": ": Write, in el name of Allah, el Beneficent, el Merciful. I heard el Messenger of Allah (s) say: “El fences of Paradise are made of gold, silver, and ruby. Its mortar is of musk and its embellishments are of red, green, and yellow sapphire.” I said: What about its gates? He said: Its gates are different. El Gate of Mercy is of red sapphire. I said: What about its door pulls? He said: Woe to you, leave me, for I have given you excess. I said: I will not leave you until you give me what you heard from el Messenger of Allah (s) regarding that. He said: Write, in el name of Allah, el Beneficent, el Merciful. As for el Gate of Patience, it is a small gate with a single door, which is [Traducción]",
